[8] Key takeaways
  • A SHA-256 manifest costs 5 lines of code and prevents hours of debugging
  • Record the training run IN the manifest immediately after saving the model
  • Set a retention deadline at dataset creation — retrofitting is painful
  • The manifest is your audit trail: dataset version → model → eval scores

Done.
